a:5:{s:5:"title";s:58:"Spiro tweaks activity timeline timestamps for readability";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:402:"<p>Recent timeline entries now display the time (rather than the year), while older entries from previous years continue to display the year. The change is intended to make “what happened today/this week” easier to scan.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
